                    Text(
                      _getCurrentTime(),
                      style: TextStyle(
                        color: Colors.white,
                        fontSize: 14,
                      ),
                    ),
                  ],
                ),
              ),
              
              // Message list
              _isLoadingChat
                ? Expanded(
                    child: Center(
                      child: CircularProgressIndicator(),
                    ),
                  )
                : Expanded(
                    child: _messages.isEmpty
                      ? Center(
                          child: Column(
                            mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.center,
                            children: [
                              Icon(Icons.chat_bubble_outline, size: 80, color: Colors.grey[300]),
                              SizedBox(height: 16),
